videos.description: Utah running back Zack Moss takes the pitch and scores the 7-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Utah RB takes the pitch and scores

videos.description: Stanford running back Trevor Speights who is filling in for the injured Bryce Love scores from 2 yards out.
videos.headline: Stanford RB powers his way into the end zone for TD

videos.headline: Stanford WR is wide open in the end zone for TD

videos.description: Utah quarterback Tyler Huntley avoids the sack then finds Samson Nacua for the 57-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Utah QB avoids sack then finds WR for TD
